include, as shareholders, Kleinwort Benson, Hambros, Robert Fleming, M&amp;G and
Henderson Administration.
Hispano Suiza was undone by the recession in the Spanish construction
industry which forced Ofirex, its construction machinery distributor, into
receivership last year.
